rComments: Just a super awesome professor. So kind and led discussions very well in this seminar class. He provided examples of exactly what he was looking for in each assignment. No final exam, just a lot of reading, and you get the most out of the course when you participate in the weekly discussions. I hope he teaches more courses at uOttawa in the future.
